<topic id='supporting_definition_overseas_visitor_treatment_portal.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Supporting Information: Overseas Visitor Treatment Portal - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_overseas_visitor_treatment_portal">Overseas Visitor Treatment Portal</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_overseas_visitor_treatment_portal">OVT Portal</xref>) is used to report treatments of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_overseas_visitor">Overseas Visitors</xref>
 (including planned treatment) from the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_european_economic_area">European Economic Area</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_european_economic_area">EEA</xref>) and Switzerland.        </p>
    <p>
      <i>
Note: There is no requirement to report treatments for 
                  <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_overseas_visitor">Overseas Visitors</xref>
 from outside the 
                  <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_european_economic_area">European Economic Area</xref>
 and Switzerland via the 
                  <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_overseas_visitor_treatment_portal">Overseas Visitor Treatment Portal</xref>.            </i>
    </p>
    <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_overseas_visitor_treatment_portal">Overseas Visitor Treatment Portal</xref>:        </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>
see the 
                          <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_department_of_health_and_social_care">Department of Health and Social Care</xref>
 guidance at: 
                          <xref href="https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/181895/Tutorial.pdf" scope="external" format="html">NHS Overseas Visitor Portal: A tutorial on how to report treatments of visitors (including planned treatment) from the EEA and Switzerland</xref>;                </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
email: 
                          <xref href="mailto:OHT.Overseasvisitorsteam@dwp.gsi.gov.uk" scope="external" format="html">OHT.Overseasvisitorsteam@dwp.gsi.gov.uk</xref>;                </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>telephone: 0191 218 1999.
      </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
